Test stopped. Select Start to start the test.
The Test is Complete

1) The System Test involves opening both the injector and shutoff valve and injecting 300ml of fuel within 2.5 minutes allowing detection of problems with the aftertreatment system.
2) The Aftertreatment Shutoff Valve Test involves opening the injector and closing the shutoff valve allowing detection of problems with the shutoff valve.
3) The Aftertreatment Injector Leak Test involves opening the shutoff valve and closing the injector allowing detection of a leaking injector.

Initial Conditions
1. Engine must be running.
Steps
1. Select Test Mode.
The Test has successfully completed. Please verify the results.
